# Text Elements
Za's strategies for waiting mode:

    1. Do all the necessary preparation for the WOT* as soon as waiting mode starts
    2. Plan a waiting mode activity - 
                    Plan for 1) transition time to get into the waiting mode activity,
                                2) what the transition mode activity will be
                                3) transition time to go from the waiting mode activity to the WOT
                                4) Head out for the WOT early
    3. Do mental preparation (i.e. playing thrugh the WOT event in your head) as needed
    4. Meditate
    5. Brain dump/journal about the WOT event
    6. set a timer/alarm so you don't forget to check the time, when you know when to head out, 
        when to start getting ready, and when to mentally check into the "going to the WOT"
        soon "mode"
    7. maybe try that new exercise strategy thingy I learned abouttttttttttttttttt
